room_title: Escape room "Titanic - The Final Hour" by Odyssey Escape Game in Atlanta
room_address: 1111 Alderman Drive Building 200, Suite 210 Alpharetta, GA 30005
room_description: Today you get to be the captain of the infamous Titanic! Joined by your crew, you must take all the necessary evacuation steps, which are: seal the water tight doors, radio for help, put on your lifejackets; release the davits and get every woman and child into the lifeboats. Try not to panic as the water rises, the fate of the passengers depends on you.
